introduction: From turf wars, to food fights, to mating mayhem, nature is all about competition and the quest to be the best. Every day, our planet is a battleground as animals go head to head with their own kind, in Battle of the Alphas.Episodes include…1. Madagascar2. Australia3. Savanna4. India5. Coastal Waters6. Canada7. South America8. Southeast Asia9. USA10. Europe11. South Africa12. Sub Sahara
